    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(0.50)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.21)) - 0.37)
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = 0.68
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.85 / v1 + 0.01) * (tmp + 0.45 - v1 + 0.74)) + wp.exp(v1))
    v0 = 0.41
